  ChevronLeft, ChevronRight, Play, RotateCw, Volume2, 
  Monitor, Clock, LogOut, SkipForward, Zap, PenTool, Eraser,
  Eye, RefreshCw, Check, BarChart2, ArrowLeft, ArrowRight,
